data.description: Within walking distance of Washburn University, priced below county appraisal. With a spacious main floor featuring a sitting area, living room, dining room and a large primary bedroom boasting two closets, including a generous walk-in. Bedroom two is on the second floor with plenty of natural light. The unfinished attic provides ample storage or an opportunity for added square footage. Single car garage off of the alley. Sold AS IS, this property awaits your personal touch and TLC.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to customize a space in a charming neighborhood!  Required Disclaimer:  Photos may be enhanced for marketing purposes.
